Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.44,0:01:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,王都入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.92,0:01:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是與魔人族利益一致的中村惠裡一手策劃的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.36,0:01:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,她使用自己的天職降靈術
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.36,0:01:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,推測她是在奧爾庫斯大迷宮遇見的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.72,0:01:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,魔人族女人遺體上留下訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.96,0:01:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,從而成功接觸了魔人族
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.92,0:02:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,然後 她以王都的詭計 殺害異世界人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.26,0:02:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,外加獻上騎士團為條件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,找魔人族換得了自己和天之河光輝的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.96,0:02:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,她之所以沒有一舉殺光自己的同伴們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,推測是因為受限於縛魂這種魔法的性質
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,只能單獨在人死亡之後立刻使用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.32,0:02:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,最後 王都入侵以失敗告終
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,中村惠裡和魔人族逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,關於陛下被洗腦並殺害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.44,0:02:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,兇手並非中村惠裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.25,0:02:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,推測與帶走畑田愛子的神山修女有關
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.36,0:02:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但目前 修女的去向未知
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,情報還在收集中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,0:03:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,異世界人犧牲者有檜山大介 近藤禮一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,還有白崎香織三人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.24,0:03:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,老師呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.80,0:03:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我們先讓老師去休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.16,0:03:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不用擔心香織 你去找愛子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.48,0:03:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:03:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,南雲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不用衝著我笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我又殺害了老師最愛的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.76,0:04:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你明白我在說誰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.32,0:04:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,說實話 我沒辦法輕易接受現實
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.52,0:04:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然檜山的所作所為的確無法饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.04,0:04:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但我也希望能讓他活著贖罪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 我也理解南雲心中的憤怒有多深重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,何況 我也沒資格教訓你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,老師你只是幫了我們一點忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.28,0:04:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,沒必要把這一切都算在自己身上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我做好了他們可能會被殺害的心理準備
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,才去幫助了緹奧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你後悔了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.32,0:04:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.68,0:05:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,當時我已下定決心 才和緹奧小姐一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我無法饒恕教會犯下的罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.48,0:05:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我決定幫你也是因為
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.64,0:05:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,如果放任不管 學生們也可能慘遭不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 我不後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,老師 你會一直當我們的老師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你願意繼續當我們的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,能不能聽聽學生的無理請求呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.84,0:05:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,無理請求嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望老師能心懷罪惡感
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,希望老師能背負著這份重量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,正確地戰鬥 正確地肩負
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,正確地煩惱 正確地示弱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,像一個普通人一樣 閃耀著些許光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:06:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,對我而言這些已經是無法觸及的感情了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你就當個榜樣教我不忘人類本性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我會認真學習的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.52,0:06:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣一來等我回了日本
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.24,0:06:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,一定也能像個普通人一樣繼續生活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,南雲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 要是你實在承受不住想要放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,實在找不到可以依靠的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.00,0:06:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我願意把後背借給你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你這人真是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就稍微借用一下吧 南雲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.12,0:06:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好嘞 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.20,0:07:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.64,0:07:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了 光輝同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,莉莉 我不辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你才辛苦了 最近五天都沒怎麼睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這點程度而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然我們也很辛苦 但真正痛苦的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是那些失去了心愛的人和財產的海利希國民
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.71,0:07:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,要是這麼說 那莉莉的陛下也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.92,0:07:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,雫的狀態怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.24,0:07:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,還是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,平時雖然跟往常一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.72,0:07:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不經意間她就會一直仰望著天空
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,在等他們回來對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.96,0:07:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,說實話 我無法信任南雲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我不希望雫和他見面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,光輝 快看 是不是有什麼東西掉下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你突然說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,大家小心 有人從天上過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,南雲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,八重檻 精神還不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,南雲 香織呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼沒見香織
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,她馬上就來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,只是她的樣貌稍微有一點點變化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.24,0:09:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我的錯 你別生我的氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.48,0:09:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.20,0:09:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在超級擔心 到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.56,0:09:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你對香織做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.08,0:09:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,始親
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這聲音是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,快接住我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋 你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.64,0:09:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,雫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:09:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,香…織
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.40,0:10:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你是香織嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.44,0:10:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 就是我香織
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,雫最好的朋友白崎香織
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.52,0:10:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然樣貌有點不太一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.24,0:10:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但也是活蹦亂跳的我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.32,0:10:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,香織
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.76,0:10:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,香織
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉讓你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事了 沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.68,0:10:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.72,0:10:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,然後呢 這到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,簡而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.36,0:10:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我們用魔法把香織的靈魂保護起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:11:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,固定在了修復之後的諾因身體裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.52,0:11:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此 完全不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.84,0:11:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 雫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我們現在使用的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.24,0:11:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是神代時期魔法的劣質版
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我們一起學習過對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.56,0:11:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 這世界的創世神話裡出現過的魔法對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.88,0:11:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,區別於現在的屬性魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.92,0:11:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,能夠作用於更底層的原理…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 難道你們使用神代魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,能夠干涉人的靈魂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.20,0:11:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.40,0:11:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 你們保護著已經死去的香織的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.04,0:11:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,把她固定在了別人的身體裡對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 不愧是雫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.48,0:11:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 為什麼是這副身體
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.36,0:11:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,香織的身體已經不能用了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.24,0:11:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,香織的身體已經完全恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.68,0:11:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,而且也成功把靈魂固定回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是我拜託他這麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:12:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我希望能變得更強
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,反正香織說過的話誰都攔不住對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,香織本來的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,用魔法冷凍起來保管好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.52,0:12:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,想回去的話隨時都可以回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.36,0:12:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.36,0:12:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然香織以前也經常亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,這次可真是太嚇人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.92,0:12:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉讓你們擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.08,0:12:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係 知道你還活著就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.28,0:12:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,南雲 月 希婭 緹奧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你們救了我最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,這份恩情我永生難忘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.92,0:12:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,有任何事情需要我幫忙 隨時吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定會竭力相助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.32,0:12:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你還是這麼重情義啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.88,0:12:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不用這麼在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我們只是救了我們自己的同伴而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:13:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但你多少也照顧過我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.24,0:13:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,為了光輝 還把重要的秘藥留給了他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你有什麼三長兩短
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,香織肯定會折騰個不停的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.84,0:13:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,折騰？你真過分 始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,某位老師對我說過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不應該選擇如此寂寞的生存方式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然不能完全照做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.84,0:13:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不過這點小事還是可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.36,0:13:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,南雲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你胡扯些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,難道說我們一直被神玩弄於股掌之間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.76,0:13:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那你為什麼不早點告訴我們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我告訴你 你就會相信我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.48,0:13:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我說神發瘋了 你做的事情都毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.40,0:13:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,別說相信我 你們首先不是會詆毀我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.44,0:13:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 今後我們還要並肩戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.84,0:14:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.28,0:14:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不打算大費周章去找他們打架
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.24,0:14:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,難道說 你要對這世界的人見死不救嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,為了素不相識的人出手相助
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.36,0:14:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我可沒那能耐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼啊 你不是比我更強嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.68,0:14:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你有能力 不應該為了正義而戰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.64,0:14:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,既然我有能力 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,正因為如此 你總會在關鍵時刻爬不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不是因為有能力才戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,而是因為要戰鬥 所以才尋求力量 使用力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.60,0:14:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你的這種意志太薄弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.52,0:15:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,就這樣放著他們不管了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,老師也陪著他們 沒關係的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,就這麼和他們分別 你不在乎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,雫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,香織 可以坐你旁邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.36,0:15:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,當然歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.76,0:15:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾一下坐在姐姐旁邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.52,0:15:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼是姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.32,0:15:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,南雲 你們接下來要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.68,0:15:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,要去大迷宮對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 東邊的大樹海 那裡有大迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.08,0:15:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 你們要穿過帝國領地嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:15:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,應該是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,既然這樣 可否讓我同行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.28,0:16:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,經歷這次王都入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,需要與帝國交涉的問題堆積如山
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,希望會談能夠早日進行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,送你過去倒是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.84,0:16:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不過我們不會進帝都
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,陪你和皇帝會談更是想都別想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.28,0:16:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不會提這麼厚臉皮的請求啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.36,0:16:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們也跟著一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.76,0:16:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,像他這種滿嘴不在乎這世界存亡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能把莉莉託付給他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.24,0:16:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,途中的警戒由我們負責
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.52,0:16:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,既然南雲無動於衷 那就由我來拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,為此我需要更強的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,需要神代魔法的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.08,0:16:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,只要跟著你走 就能獲得神代魔法對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 我告訴你地方你自己去唄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.68,0:16:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,非要跟著我們簡直添了個大麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,可是南雲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:17:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你說過現在的我們就算去挑戰大迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.28,0:17:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,也只是去送命而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.76,0:17:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,這個嘛 其實就是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.76,0:17:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你看我這麼廢物都熬過來了 問題不大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的 你們可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.04,0:17:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,果然還是不太行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.16,0:17:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,帶我們去一次就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.92,0:17:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕擁有一種神代魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.88,0:17:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,攻略其他迷宮時就會有天壤之別
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.16,0:17:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,鈴也拜託你了 南雲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.36,0:17:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,鈴也想變得更強 再去找惠裡談一談
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.96,0:17:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託你了 南雲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我也希望得到能保護自己和同伴的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.52,0:17:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,南雲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,黎明我們就出發
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.68,0:17:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 南雲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我們一定會攻略大迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.88,0:18:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,始大人 這樣真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,帶上他們只會給我添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.88,0:18:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不過帶上他們一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.16,0:18:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,讓他們跟著變強也是個不錯的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,始 真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.80,0:18:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,思維已經超乎常人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,把同學當肉盾兼誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.16,0:18:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.32,0:18:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,始大人 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.44,0:18:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.28,0:18:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,主人 我的也吃一口 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,就這一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:18:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.72,0:18:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼氛圍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.88,0:19:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,尷尬得要命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.95,0:19:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,變態
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.24,0:19:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是 你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是正常吃飯而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.24,0:19:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴上這麼說 心裡卻在品嘗始的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.84,0:19:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,才沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.80,0:19:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,再說了 要說的話緹奧才是變態吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 這就光明正大開始舔叉子了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,緹奧 你給我立刻住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法呀 主人至今不肯與妾身接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.16,0:19:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,主人 請求獎勵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.32,0:19:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,妾身保護了老師 給點獎勵又何妨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.96,0:19:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼說辭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,真不講理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.32,0:19:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.72,0:19:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,先說好 只准提我能辦得到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:20:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,放心 不會為難主人的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.56,0:20:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,小事 就像我們初次見面時一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,玩弄妾身的屁股就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.36,0:20:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼 這點要求不過分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,像當初一樣用大黑粗貫穿妾身的屁股就行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,別說這種讓人誤會的話了行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 也不能說完全是誤會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,的確沒說假話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.96,0:20:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,確實是插進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 南雲當時毫不留情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.76,0:20:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,始大人 說誤會好像是有點不太對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.64,0:20:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,始 緹奧開始變態的原因就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.44,0:20:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,接受現實吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,南雲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.68,0:20:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你這人到底對緹奧小姐做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.48,0:21:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,OK 緹奧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那就給你來點獎勵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.52,0:21:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,比當初更粗更硬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.36,0:21:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,而且是加重版的自信之作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.40,0:21:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.64,0:21:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛說的那些只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.20,0:21:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,別客氣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.32,0:21:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你嬌喘都來不及 一發入魂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.68,0:21:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,主人的眼神是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,月 希婭 香織 快阻止主人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.68,0:21:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.96,0:21:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.52,0:22:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,看來今天也不會好過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.32,0:22:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,趕緊結束旅程 去接繆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.52,0:22:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.64,0:22:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你們兩個又單獨約會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.80,0:22:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,每次都是月 真過分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.36,0:22:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.40,0:22:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好了南雲 趕緊出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.72,0:22:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,大迷宮 一定要攻略成功
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.32,0:22:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,迫不及待了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.68,0:22:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你們太興奮了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.40,0:22:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,南雲 要託你多照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.60,0:23:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,王都的事情就交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.92,0:23:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,大家一定要平安
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.36,0:23:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,老師你們也是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.72,0:23:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我們走吧
Comment: 0,0:00:01.89,0:00:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-----------------OP-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.12,0:00:23.66,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Tears streaming down your sorrow face
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:29.67,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Came a long and painful road, you gave yourself away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.50,0:00:35.01,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You saw everything, heaven to hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:41.43,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You say you need a self redemption, to mend the broken wings
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.93,0:00:46.85,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Drowning in the dark, no place to be
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.56,0:00:50.61,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}But I am by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.90,0:00:52.44,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You’re not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.69,0:00:58.37,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Daylight, shed a light so you won’t disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.57,0:01:04.33,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Cause I know where you belong, save your saddened heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.33,0:01:10.04,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}With a flashback, screaming out but still we’re holding on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.21,0:01:15.47,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Waiting for the break of dawn for a new day to begin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.92,0:01:18.72,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Daylight, daylight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.30,0:01:24.06,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Stay a little while longer
Comment: 0,0:22:09.97,0:22:10.01,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,------------------ED------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.39,0:22:18.73,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an7\fscx75\fscy75}全部　期待してみて幻だった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:23.23,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an7\fscx75\fscy75}信じたかった　縋りたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.15,0:22:29.95,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an7\fscx75\fscy75}身体の底に開いた螺旋状の穴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.24,0:22:35.12,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an7\fscx75\fscy75}ボクだけじゃなく　キミにもなんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.58,0:22:44.30,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an7\fscx75\fscy75}許されることなど　もう望んじゃいない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:48.84,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an7\fscx75\fscy75}抱き寄せてもまた　わからないシルエット
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.84,0:22:53.39,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an7\fscx75\fscy75}躊躇いもなく傷つけた代償か
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.64,0:22:58.52,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an7\fscx75\fscy75}キミの側は　揺れてボクを離れた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.52,0:23:03.48,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an7\fscx75\fscy75}どちらが欲しいかなんて　残酷な問い神様は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.48,0:23:08.07,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an7\fscx75\fscy75}何度ボクらに投げかける
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.07,0:23:13.07,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an7\fscx75\fscy75}道を違える度に　ボクの後ろに穴が開く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.07,0:23:16.12,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an7\fscx75\fscy75}伸びた一本の影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.41,0:23:22.58,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an7\fscx75\fscy75}誰もが手にし得る　小さな欠片で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.83,0:23:27.17,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an7\fscx75\fscy75}何ができる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.17,0:23:32.34,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an7\fscx75\fscy75}どちらが欲しいかなんて　残酷な問い神様は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.34,0:23:37.18,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an7\fscx75\fscy75}何度ボクらに投げかける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.39,0:22:18.73,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an7\fscx75\fscy75}期待的一切皆為虛空一場
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:23.23,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an7\fscx75\fscy75}破滅的希望　虛偽的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.15,0:22:29.95,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an7\fscx75\fscy75}嵌入身體的傷口深不見底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.24,0:22:35.12,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an7\fscx75\fscy75}不僅是我　你也背負同樣的傷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.58,0:22:44.30,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an7\fscx75\fscy75}早已不再奢望　求得誰人原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:48.84,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an7\fscx75\fscy75}哪怕懷中相擁　徒留輪廓難辨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.84,0:22:53.39,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an7\fscx75\fscy75}甘願承傷不曾猶豫的代價
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.64,0:22:58.52,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an7\fscx75\fscy75}我步履蹣跚　忍痛離開你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.52,0:23:03.48,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an7\fscx75\fscy75}神明凜然在上　拋下兩難抉擇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.48,0:23:08.07,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an7\fscx75\fscy75}不斷拷問你我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.07,0:23:13.07,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an7\fscx75\fscy75}幾步對錯　令我身負百孔千瘡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.07,0:23:16.12,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an7\fscx75\fscy75}形單影隻漸行漸遠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.41,0:23:22.58,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an7\fscx75\fscy75}希望碎片　誰人不曾擁有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.83,0:23:27.17,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an7\fscx75\fscy75}又能作何掙扎
